@@TJvStrToHtml
<TITLEIMG TJvStrToHtml>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.Miscel, JVCL.Internet.ConvertersAndParsers.HTML
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  Component that can convert a string into a form that contains no values that are illegal in an HTML
  document.
Description
  Use TJvStrToHTML when you need to convert a string into valid HTML or convert HTML to a valid
  string.
  Use the Text and Html properties to perform the conversion using properties. To convert any
  arbitrary string, use HtmlToText and TextToHtml instead.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvStrToHtml.Html
Summary
  Contains the HTML string.
Description
  \Read Html to convert the content of Text to HTML. Write to Html and then \read Text to access the
  value of Html as a plain string.
See Also
  TJvStrToHtml.Text

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvStrToHtml.HtmlToText
Summary
  Converts an HTML string to plain text.
Description
  Use HtmlToText to convert special HTML characters to plain text characters.
Parameters
  Text - The text to convert.
Return value
  The converted text.
See Also
  TJvStrToHtml.TextToHtml

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvStrToHtml.Text
Summary
  Contains the plain text string.
Description
  \Read Text to convert Html to plain text. Write to Text and then \read Html to access the value of
  Text as a HTML string.
See Also
  TJvStrToHtml.Html

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvStrToHtml.TextToHtml
Summary
  Converts a plain string to an HTML string.
Description
  Use TextToHtml to convert plain text characters to special HTML characters.
Parameters
  Text - The text to convert.
Return value
  The converted text.
See Also
  TJvStrToHtml.HtmlToText

